玛丽亚·凯莉冷落摇滚名人堂：“我的律师比我先进入” https://www.nme.com/news/music/mariah-carey-on-rock-roll-hall-of-fame-snub-my-lawyer-got-in-before-me-3809162?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=玛丽亚·凯莉在摇滚名人堂冷落我的律师在我之前就加入了Surej SinghMon, 04 Nov 2024 03:57:12 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopR&B https://www.nme.com/?p=3809162 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-carey@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-carey@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-carey@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-carey@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-carey@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-carey@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-carey@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>艾伦·格鲁曼 (Allen Grubman) 曾担任 U2、埃尔顿·约翰 (Elton John) 等人的律师，于 2022 年入职</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mariah-carey-on-rock-roll-hall-of-fame-snub-my-lawyer-got-in-before-me-3809162">玛丽亚·凯莉 (Mariah Carey) 冷落摇滚名人堂的帖子：“我的律师在我之前进入”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-carey@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-carey@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-carey@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-carey@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-carey@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-carey@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-carey@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mariah-carey">玛丽亚·凯莉</a>公开谈论了自己被摇滚名人堂冷落的经历——看看下面她是怎么说的。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/mariah-carey-cover-interview-2021-fall-in-love-at-christmas-3120794">玛丽亚·凯莉：“你知道吗？我喜欢圣诞节！”</a></strong></li></ul><p>自从 20 世纪 80 年代末和 90 年代初在音乐界崭露头角以来，玛丽亚·凯莉 (Mariah Carey) 发行了许多专辑，打破了一系列记录并多次获得冠军。然而，这位《We Belong Together》歌手却一次又一次地错过了摇滚名人堂中令人垂涎的一席之地。</p><p>凯莉自 2016 年起就有资格入读， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-roll-hall-of-fame-2024-oasis-ozzy-osbourne-and-mariah-carey-among-nominees-3585620">今年早些时候首次获得提名</a>，但最终未能在 2024 届毕业生中获得一席之地，该届毕业生包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cher">雪儿</a>(Cher)、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ozzy-osbourne">奥兹·奥斯本 (Ozzy Osbourne)</a>等人。 </p><figure id="attachment_3808777" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3808777" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3808777" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-Carey-@-2000-x-1270.jpg" alt="玛丽亚·凯莉在全美音乐奖上表演。图片来源：Michael Buckner/Penske Media via Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-Carey-@-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-Carey-@-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-Carey-@-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-Carey-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-Carey-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mariah-Carey-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3808777" class="wp-caption-text">玛丽亚·凯莉在全美音乐奖上表演。图片来源：Michael Buckner/Penske Media via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>凯里最近在接受《 <a href="https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/music/story/2024-10-30/mariah-carey-all-i-want-for-christmas-is-you-tour-interview" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>洛杉矶时报》</em></a>采访时被问及提名。她坦率地回答道：“我的想法是，我没有进去。每个人都打电话给我，说，‘我想你进去了！’所以我对此感到兴奋。但后来这一切并没有发生。我的律师比我先进入摇滚名人堂。”</p><p>她的律师艾伦·格鲁曼（Allen Grubman）是摇滚名人堂的联合创始人，于 2022 年入选。格鲁曼长期以来一直是明星的律师，代理过娱乐界的多个大牌，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀（Bruce Springsteen）</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/u2">U2</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sting">斯汀（Sting</a> ）、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madonna">麦当娜</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">埃尔顿·约翰</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>等。</p><p>虽然格鲁曼作为一名律师的角色在<a href="https://rockhall.com/inductees/allen-grubman/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">摇滚名人堂“为他的客户谈判突破性的长期协议，使他们能够保持对自己作品的创造性控制”方面发挥了重要作用，但他进入摇滚名人堂的</a>经历却并非如此。这个决定得到了一些同事的一致好评。 </p><figure id="attachment_3809167" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3809167" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3809167" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/allen-grubman@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/allen-grubman@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/allen-grubman@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/allen-grubman@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/allen-grubman@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/allen-grubman@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/allen-grubman@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3809167" class="wp-caption-text">艾伦·格鲁曼 (Allen Grubman) 出席 2022 年摇滚名人堂入会仪式。图片来源：Christopher Polk/Variety via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> 2022 年，摇滚厅和<em>滚石乐队</em>联合创始人詹恩·温纳 (Jann Wenner) <a href="https://www.stereogum.com/2203213/rock-hall-co-founder-jann-wenner-protests-induction-of-lawyer-who-has-not-made-one-iota-of-difference-in-music-history/news/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">透露，他不喜欢格鲁曼的入职</a>，称这位律师“从任何定义来看，都没有对摇滚乐的创意发展或历史做出任何形式的贡献”。卷。他之所以被选中是因为他作为娱乐界超级律师的影响力。这个决定关乎金钱和屈服于音乐行业权力掮客的自负。”</p><p>据<a href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/jann-wenner-protesting-allen-grubman-rock-hall-fame-induction/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《公告牌》</em></a>报道，温纳进一步说道：“在我辞职后，我被告知董事会中的音乐界权力掮客将被引入。这些人对音乐创作的历史、现在或未来没有造成丝毫影响，这是明确的标准。但他们积累了影响力和财富。这是一项内部工作。” </p><figure id="attachment_3782515" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3782515" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3782515" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Mariah-Carey.-Credit-Denise-Truscello.jpg" alt="玛丽亚·凯莉。图片来源：丹尼斯·特鲁塞洛" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Mariah-Carey.-Credit-Denise-Truscello.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Mariah-Carey.-Credit-Denise-Truscello-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Mariah-Carey.-Credit-Denise-Truscello-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Mariah-Carey.-Credit-Denise-Truscello-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Mariah-Carey.-Credit-Denise-Truscello-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Mariah-Carey.-Credit-Denise-Truscello-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3782515" class="wp-caption-text">玛丽亚·凯莉。图片来源：丹尼斯·特鲁塞洛</figcaption></figure><p>温纳本人于 2004 年因其对音乐新闻的贡献而入选摇滚名人堂，并于 2023 年在一次有争议的采访后被从摇滚名人堂董事会除名，他在采访中表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jann-wenner-says-female-and-black-artists-not-intellectual-enough-to-be-interviewed-for-his-new-book-3498935">女性和黑人艺术家“不够聪明”，无法</a>接受采访他的书<em>《大师》</em> 。</p><p>玛丽亚·凯莉并不是唯一一位一直未能入选摇滚名人堂的音乐家。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-roll-hall-of-fame-2024-cher-says-she-changed-the-sound-of-music-forever-3804371">上个月终于入选的</a>雪儿在 2023 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cher-hits-out-at-rock-roll-hall-of-fame-after-repeated-snubs-3559731">谈到了自己缺席摇滚厅的经历，</a>尽管她在 1990 年就获得了入选资格：“他们只能自己做，你知道的。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mariah-carey-on-rock-roll-hall-of-fame-snub-my-lawyer-got-in-before-me-3809162">玛丽亚·凯莉 (Mariah Carey) 冷落摇滚名人堂的帖子：“我的律师在我之前进入”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
