ny-marr-refutes-claims-of-ignoring-the-smiths-reunion-offer-3795376">莫里西解雇了他的管理团队</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-show-in-dallas-cut-short-after-fans-invade-stage-3809106">莫里西在达拉斯的演出因粉丝闯入舞台而缩短，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
